SELECT j."Id", j."AccountId", j."ActualLaborHours", j."AssignedToId", j."CompletedAt", j."CreatedAt", j."CustomerId", j."Description", j."EndTime", j."EstimatedLaborHours", j."JobType", j."Location", j."LocationLat", j."LocationLng", j."Notes", j."ScheduledDate", j."ScheduledTime", j."StartTime", j."Status", j."Title", j."UpdatedAt", c."Id", c."AccountId", c."Address", c."City", c."Country", c."CreatedAt", c."Email", c."FirstName", c."IsActive", c."LastName", c."Notes", c."PhoneNumber", c."PostalCode", c."State", c."UpdatedAt", j0."Id", j0."CreatedAt", j0."Description", j0."JobId", j0."MaterialType", j0."Quantity", j0."ReceiptImageUrl", j0."SupplierName", j0."TotalCost", j0."UnitPrice", j0."UpdatedAt"
FROM "Jobs" AS j
INNER JOIN "Customers" AS c ON j."CustomerId" = c."Id"

    SELECT j."Id", j."AccountId", j."ActualLaborHours", j."AssignedToId", j."CompletedAt", j."CreatedAt", j."CustomerId", j."Description", j."EndTime", j."EstimatedLaborHours", j."JobType", j."Location", j."LocationLat", j."LocationLng", j."Notes", j."ScheduledDate", j."ScheduledTime", j."StartTime", j."Status", j."Title", j."UpdatedAt"
    FROM "Jobs" AS j
    ORDER BY j."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
INNER JOIN "Customers" AS c ON t."CustomerId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "JobMaterials" AS j0 ON t."Id" = j0."JobId"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC, t."Id", c."Id"

FROM (
    SELECT j."Id", j."AccountId", j."ActualLaborHours", j."AssignedToId", j."CompletedAt", j."CreatedAt", j."CustomerId", j."Description", j."EndTime", j."EstimatedLaborHours", j."JobType", j."Location", j."LocationLat", j."LocationLng", j."Notes", j."ScheduledDate", j."ScheduledTime", j."StartTime", j."Status", j."Title", j."UpdatedAt"

    ORDER BY j."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t

) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."AccountId", t."ActualLaborHours", t."AssignedToId", t."CompletedAt", t."CreatedAt", t."CustomerId", t."Description", t."EndTime", t."EstimatedLaborHours", t."JobType", t."Location", t."LocationLat", t."LocationLng", t."Notes", t."ScheduledDate", t."ScheduledTime", t."StartTime", t."Status", t."Title", t."UpdatedAt", c."Id", c."AccountId", c."Address", c."City", c."Country", c."CreatedAt", c."Email", c."FirstName", c."IsActive", c."LastName", c."Notes", c."PhoneNumber", c."PostalCode", c."State", c."UpdatedAt", j0."Id", j0."CreatedAt", j0."Description", j0."JobId", j0."MaterialType", j0."Quantity", j0."ReceiptImageUrl", j0."SupplierName", j0."TotalCost", j0."UnitPrice", j0."UpdatedAt"

    SELECT j."Id", j."AccountId", j."ActualLaborHours", j."AssignedToId", j."CompletedAt", j."CreatedAt", j."CustomerId", j."Description", j."EndTime", j."EstimatedLaborHours", j."JobType", j."Location", j."LocationLat", j."LocationLng", j."Notes", j."ScheduledDate", j."ScheduledTime", j."StartTime", j."Status", j."Title", j."UpdatedAt"
    FROM "Jobs" AS j
    ORDER BY j."CreatedAt" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS t
INNER JOIN "Customers" AS c ON t."CustomerId" = c."Id"
LEFT JOIN "JobMaterials" AS j0 ON t."Id" = j0."JobId"
ORDER BY t."CreatedAt" DESC, t."Id", c."Id"
